        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "executive_summary",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### Executive Summary\n",
                "\n",
                "**Customer Base Overview**: The Bank of Fiction serves **10,000 customers** across three European markets (France, Germany, Spain), with France representing approximately 50% of the total customer base.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Key Financial Insights**:\n",
                "* Average customer salary of **€100K** indicates a premium banking segment\n",
                "* Income distribution shows balanced segmentation across low, mid, and high-income brackets\n",
                "* Geographic consistency in financial profiles suggests effective market positioning\n",
                "\n",
                "**Customer Quality Metrics**:\n",
                "* Average credit score of **650** demonstrates solid creditworthiness across the portfolio\n",
                "* Customer tenure averaging **5 years** indicates strong retention and relationship stability\n",
                "* Balanced mix of new, established, and loyal customers ensures sustainable growth\n",
                "\n",
                "**Strategic Implications**: The portfolio demonstrates healthy diversification across geographies with consistent quality metrics, positioning the bank well for continued growth in the European market."
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 7,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 7
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "problem_statement",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### Problem Statement & Analysis Objectives\n",
                "\n",
                "**Business Context**: As the Bank of Fiction expands its operations across three European markets, leadership requires comprehensive visibility into customer portfolio composition, financial profiles, and relationship quality to inform strategic growth decisions.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Key Business Questions**:\n",
                "* How is our customer base distributed across geographies, and what are the demographic characteristics?\n",
                "* What is the financial profile of our customers, and how does income segmentation vary by market?\n",
                "* How strong are our customer relationships as measured by tenure and credit quality?\n",
                "* Are there meaningful differences in customer quality metrics across our European markets?\n",
                "\n",
                "**Analysis Objectives**:\n",
                "1. **Portfolio Assessment**: Quantify total customer base and geographic distribution\n",
                "2. **Financial Profiling**: Analyze income levels and salary distributions across markets\n",
                "3. **Relationship Quality**: Evaluate customer tenure, loyalty segments, and creditworthiness\n",
                "4. **Market Comparison**: Identify geographic patterns in customer composition and quality\n",
                "5. **Strategic Insights**: Provide actionable recommendations for growth and risk management"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 2,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 5
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "recommendations",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### Strategic Recommendations\n",
                "\n",
                "**1. Market Expansion Priorities**\n",
                "* **France Optimization**: With 50% market share, focus on deepening wallet share through cross-sell initiatives targeting the established high-income segment\n",
                "* **Germany & Spain Growth**: Accelerate customer acquisition in these balanced markets (25% each) where infrastructure investment can yield proportional returns\n",
                "* **Income Segmentation Strategy**: Develop targeted products for each income tier, particularly premium services for the high-income segment across all geographies\n",
                "\n",
                "**2. Customer Retention & Loyalty Enhancement**\n",
                "* **Tenure-Based Programs**: Implement graduated loyalty benefits starting at 3 years to convert new customers to established status\n",
                "* **Geographic Retention Focus**: Analyze churn patterns by market to identify region-specific retention levers\n",
                "* **Credit Score Monitoring**: Proactive engagement with customers showing credit score declines to prevent attrition\n",
                "\n",
                "**3. Risk Management Initiatives**\n",
                "* **Credit Quality Maintenance**: Current 650 average score is solid; maintain underwriting standards while exploring opportunities in the 600-700 range\n",
                "* **Portfolio Diversification**: Balance growth across income segments to mitigate concentration risk in high-income segment\n",
                "* **Geographic Risk Balance**: Monitor macroeconomic indicators across markets to adjust exposure as needed\n",
                "\n",
                "**4. Revenue Optimization**\n",
                "* **Premium Product Development**: €100K average salary suggests strong capacity for wealth management and investment products\n",
                "* **Tenure-Based Pricing**: Reward loyal customers (5+ years) with preferential rates to enhance lifetime value\n",
                "* **Cross-Border Services**: Leverage multi-country presence to offer regional banking solutions for internationally mobile customers\n",
                "\n",
                "**5. Data & Analytics Next Steps**\n",
                "* **Predictive Analytics**: Develop churn prediction models using tenure, credit score, and engagement data\n",
                "* **Customer Segmentation Refinement**: Create micro-segments within income tiers for personalized marketing\n",
                "* **Real-Time Monitoring**: Implement automated alerts for significant portfolio metric changes by geography"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 32,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 8
          }
        },
        {
          "widget": {
            "name": "appendix",
            "multilineTextboxSpec": {
              "lines": [
                "### Appendix\n",
                "\n",
                "**A. Data Sources**\n",
                "* **Customer Demographics Summary**: `bank_of_fiction.gold.customer_demographics_summary`\n",
                "  * Contains geographic distribution, age, gender, credit scores, and tenure data\n",
                "  * Aggregated at geography level with statistical measures (averages, min/max, medians)\n",
                "* **Customer Financial Metrics**: `bank_of_fiction.gold.customer_financial_metrics`\n",
                "  * Income and salary data with percentile distributions\n",
                "  * Income segmentation categories and percentages by geography\n",
                "* **Customer Tenure Analysis**: `bank_of_fiction.gold.customer_tenure_analysis`\n",
                "  * Tenure segments (new, established, loyal) with definitions\n",
                "  * Credit score analysis by tenure segment\n",
                "\n",
                "**B. Methodology & Definitions**\n",
                "* **Income Segments**:\n",
                "  * Low Income: < €50,000 annual salary\n",
                "  * Mid Income: €50,000 - €100,000 annual salary\n",
                "  * High Income: > €100,000 annual salary\n",
                "* **Tenure Categories**:\n",
                "  * New Customers: 0-2 years with the bank\n",
                "  * Established Customers: 3-5 years with the bank\n",
                "  * Loyal Customers: 6+ years with the bank\n",
                "* **Credit Score Scale**: Standard FICO-style scoring (300-850 range)\n",
                "* **Geographic Coverage**: France, Germany, Spain (Eurozone markets)\n",
                "\n",
                "**C. Analysis Period & Assumptions**\n",
                "* Analysis Date: May 6, 2026\n",
                "* Currency: EUR (Euro) for all financial metrics\n",
                "* Data reflects active customer accounts as of analysis date\n",
                "* Aggregations computed using SQL metric views on Unity Catalog tables\n",
                "\n",
                "**D. Technical Notes**\n",
                "* Dashboard powered by 3 metric view datasets (DLMV)\n",
                "* Interactive filtering available via Geography selector\n",
                "* All percentages rounded to 2 decimal places\n",
                "* Averages calculated using arithmetic mean across all customers in segment\n",
                "\n",
                "**E. Contact & Updates**\n",
                "* Dashboard Owner: Bank of Fiction Analytics Team\n",
                "* Refresh Schedule: Updated monthly with latest customer data\n",
                "* For questions or data requests: Contact analytics@bankoffiction.eu"
              ]
            }
          },
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": 40,
            "width": 12,
            "height": 7
          }
